channel.title: I added report abuse, got these two errors. Anyone no how to fix?
channel.description:
Hi,
I added a report abuse, this is the error I got:
Hi, I only got two errors, they were:
[CODE]client.java:10: cannot find symbol symbol : class SimpleDateFormat location: class client public String date = new SimpleDateFormat("dd/MM/yyyy").format(new Date()); ^ client.java:11: cannot find symbol symbol : class SimpleDateFormat location: class client public String time = new SimpleDateFormat("hh:mm:ss").format(new Date()); ^ Note: stream.java uses or overrides a deprecated API. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:deprecation for details. 2 errors Server Compiled Successfully! Press any key to continue . . .[/CODE]
Does anyone no how to fix?
Thanks.
James
Please help
